import React from "react";
import "../assets/navbar.css";
import { Link } from "react-router-dom";

export default function Header() {
  return (
    <nav className="navbar">
      <button className="abutton active">
      <Link to="/" style={{ display: "block", height: "100%" }}>
        Home
      </Link>
      </button>
      <button className="abutton">
        <Link to="/discover" style={{ display: "block", height: "100%" }}>
          Discover
        </Link>
      </button>
      <button className="abutton">
        <Link to="/profile" style={{ display: "block", height: "100%" }}>
          Profile
        </Link>
      </button>
      <button id="createpost" className="abutton">
        <Link to="/createpost" style={{ display: "block", height: "100%" }}>
          Create Post
        </Link>
      </button>
      <button id="login" className="abutton">
        <Link to="/login" style={{ display: "block", height: "100%" }}>
          Login
        </Link>
      </button>
    </nav>
  );
}
